data.name: Welcome_Label.Text
data.value: - when creating a new item, it will be added to the end of the list of existing items. (ex. adding a new trail will make it the last trail to appear on the mobile app) - current exhibits will always be displayed before past exhibits on the mobile app - events will be displayed in chronogical order on the mobile app, no need to reorder them on this app - When a save button is clicked, all changes made on THAT screen will be save and pushed to the Google Drive - When reordering things, the top will be the first item to be displayed on the mobile app - When something is deleted, that entire item and all associates files will be permanently deleted
